msg: Tweak some tree conflicts during merge to properly report nodes missing when
they are not deleted and/or moved away.
(check_moved_away): Remove error processing. All callers know if the node
is in the db as deleted, so shouldn't perform unneeded wc.db calls.
(merge_file_changed): Only perform moved away check for deleted.
(merge_file_deleted): Handle missing, and only perform move check for
(merge_dir_deleted): Provide missing, and only perform move check for
(merge_dir_opened): Provide missing, and only perform move check for
